ECLASS:1,Nightblade=10	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadowstriker ~ Master's Armament|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=17																																																																																		COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.28	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Nightblade																																																																																																																																																																																	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique1|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_Evasion|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_NightbladeArt6|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_ImprovedEvasion|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique5|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_HideInPlainSight|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique10|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_TripleSurge|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_Evasion|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_NightbladeArt6|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_ImprovedEvasion|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_PathTechnique5|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_HideInPlainSight|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_PathTechnique10|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_TripleSurge|true
Shadow Agent										KEY:Nightblade Archetype ~ Dark Conjuror			CATEGORY:Archetype				TYPE:Archetype.NightbladeArchetype																																			PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Nightblade Archetype ~ Dark Conjuror],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Nightblade_Archetype_PathPower=true,Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique1=true,Nightblade_Archetype_NightbladeArt3=true,Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique10=true]																																																															DESC:Being able to remain unseen is a powerful tool in the hands of an assassin. With a mixture of arcane arts and lethal poisons, shadow agents can strike with swift and deadly precision, vanishing back into darkness when the job is complete.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Agent ~ Sneak Attack|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Agent ~ Poison Expertise|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Agent ~ Swift Poisoning|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=3	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Agent ~ Uncanny Dodge|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=4	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Agent ~ Assassinate|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=10	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Shadow Agent ~ Swift Assassination|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=16																																																																																																	COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.28	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Nightblade																																																																																																																																																																																	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_PathPower|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique1|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_NightbladeArt3|true	FACT:Nightblade_Archetype_PathTechnique10|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_PathPower|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_PathTechnique1|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_NightbladeArt3|true	FACT:Nightblade_CF_PathTechnique10|true
Traveler Of Two Paths									KEY:Nightblade Archetype ~ Traveler Of Two Paths	CATEGORY:Archetype				TYPE:Archetype.NightbladeArchetype																																			PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1																																																																																																											DESC:Some nightblades find themselves in need of diversifying their training, choosing to study two paths rather than one. The nightblade gains access to a mixture of the abilities of these two paths, but dividing her training causes her to lose skills in other areas.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Traveler Of Two Paths ~ Path Power|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Traveler Of Two Paths ~ Techniques|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Traveler Of Two Paths ~ Shadow Surge|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Traveler Of Two Paths ~ Nightblade Arts|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Traveler Of Two Paths ~ Drawbacks|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1																																																																																																														COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.28	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Nightblade
