Veiled Infiltrator									KEY:Nightblade Archetype ~ Veiled Infiltrator		CATEGORY:Archetype				TYPE:Archetype.NightbladeArchetype																																			PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Nightblade Archetype ~ Veiled Infiltrator],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Nightblade_Archetype_ShadowSurge=True,Nightblade_Archetype_TwinSurge=True,Nightblade_Archetype_TripleSurge=True]																																																																						DESC:It is no secret that nightblades excel at stealth, but some prefer a more practical approach. A well-known specialization among spies, thieves, and saboteurs, veiled infiltrators learn how to break into any group or stronghold with a combination of illusions, subterfuge, and their own wit.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Veiled Infiltrator ~ Trapfinding|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=1	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Veiled Infiltrator ~ Infiltrator's Veil|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=2	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Veiled Infiltrator ~ Rogue Talents|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=3	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Veiled Infiltrator ~ Trap Sense|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=3	ABILITY:Nightblade Class Feature|AUTOMATIC|Veiled Infiltrator ~ Advanced Talents|PRECLASS:1,Nightblade=12																																																																																																														COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.28	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Nightblade																																																																																																																																																