Class Skills										KEY:Darkness Mystery ~ Class Skills				CATEGORY:Special Ability			TYPE:Oracle Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																DESC:An oracle with the darkness mystery adds Bluff (Cha), Intimidate (Cha), Perception (Wis), and Stealth (Dex) to her list of class skills.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				CSKILL:Bluff|Intimidate|Perception|Stealth			SOURCEPAGE:p.32
